definitions.definition: A newspaper ; a printed sheet published periodically.
An official periodical publication published by a government containing legal and state notices, and in some cases, legislations , subsidiary legislations and bills .
definitions.label_groups: law , often capitalized and italicized in legislations

main_definition: A newspaper ; a printed sheet published periodically. [from 1605]
